<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meeting topilmadi – PDP Chat</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #ea4335;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #202124;
        }

        .error-msg {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #5f6368;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Meeting topilmadi yoki muddati o'tgan</h1>
        <p class="error-msg">
            Siz qidirayotgan majlis manzili noto'g'ri yoki u allaqachon yakunlangan bo'lishi mumkin.
            Iltimos, manzilni tekshiring yoki yangi majlis yarating.
        </p>
        <button class="btn-primary-lg" onclick="window.location.href='/'">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Bosh sahifaga qaytish
        </button>
    </div>
</body>

</html>